Offline Signature Authentication Algorithm
Overview
This repository provides an implementation of an offline signature authentication algorithm based on fuzzy set theory. The algorithm enables verification of handwritten signatures without requiring real-time connectivity.

Citation
If you use this algorithm in your research, please cite the following paper:

Qiu, Shi, Fei, Fengchang, Cui, Ying. (2021). "Offline Signature Authentication Algorithm Based on the Fuzzy Set." Mathematical Problems in Engineering, 2021, Article ID 5554341, 8 pages.
https://doi.org/10.1155/2021/5554341
